Edwin W. MISFELDT, Appellant, v. HOSPITAL AUTHORITY OF the CITY OF MARIETTA, GEORGIA, A. A. Ros-ser and Joe Barnett, Appellees. No. 20761. United States Court of Appeals Fifth Circuit. March 31, 1964. J. M. Grubbs, Jr., Jordan H. Prosser, William H. Burke, Grubbs, Prosser & Burke, Marietta, Ga., for plaintiff. Hamilton Lokey, Atlanta, Ga., Scott S. Edwards, Jr., Marietta, Ga., for ap-pellees.

Before TUTTLE, Chief Judge, WISDOM, Circuit Judge, and CARSWELL, District Judge.

PER CURIAM:

As announced from the bench in open court, the judgment of the trial court is hereby affirmed.
